quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,34,"Maaku : \"Hara no e kafidiiɓe mon ɓen on mo no fuɗɗa tagu refi o ruttita ngu [ɓaawo maayde]?\" Maaku :\"Ko Alla fuɗɗata tagu ngun refti O ruttita ngu. Ko honno fefindara ɗon [faade e meere]"
  10,35,"Maaku : \"Hara no e kafidiiɓe mon ɓen on fewnoowo e goonga?\" Maaku: \"Alla no feewna e goonga. E ko on fewnoowo e goonga ɓuri handude e jokkeede, kaa ko on mo feewantaa (hoore mon) si wanaa on fewna? Ko heɓi on sifa no ñaawirton"
  10,36,Ko ɓuri ɗuuɗude e maɓɓe jokkah si wanah sikke. Pellet sikke ɗen duncataa e goonga kan hay e huunde. Pellet Alla ko Annduɗo ko ɓe gollata
  10,37,"Sellatah ka ndee Alqur'aanaare fefindiree gaanin Alla, si ko woni, ko nde goonginnde ko woni yeeso mayre, e fensitunde deftere, sikke alaa e mayre, ko nde immorde ka Jeyɗo Winndere nden"
  10,38,"Kaa ɓe wi'ay : \"O fefindi nde?\" Maaku : \"Addee cortewol(simoore) yeru mayre, noddon kala mo haɗtanɗon gaanin Alla, si on laatike goonguɓe"
  10,39,"Ko woni, ɓe fennii ko ɓe huɓindaaki ganndal mun, [ko ɓe fenniri nde], ko nde tawnoo firo mayre araali ɓe taho. Ko wano non adinooɓe ɓen fennirnoo. Ndaaru ko honno battane tooñooɓe ɓen wa'unoo"
  10,40,"No e maɓɓe gomɗinɗo nde, no e maɓɓe kadi mo gomɗinaa nde. Ko Joomi maa ɓuri anndude bonnooɓe ɓen"
  10,41,"Si ɓe fennii ma, maaku : \"No woodani lam (njoɓdi) golle am, no woodani on (njoɓdi) kuuɗe mon. Onon ko on daɗndiiɓe ko mi gollata, min kadi ko mi daɗndiiɗo(kisdo) ko golloton"
  10,42,"No e maɓɓe ɓen heɗotooɓe ma. E ko annannta faaɗu ɓe ɓen, hay tawii ɓe haqqiltah"